{%- assign wa_general = 'https://wa.me/31624978746?text=Hoi%20Pixel!%20Ik%20heb%20een%20vraag%20over%20een%20bestelling.' -%}

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-50 via-white to-emerald-50 border-b border-slate-200">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 opacity-60">
    <div class="absolute top-10 right-10 w-80 h-80 rounded-full bg-emerald-200/40 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-10 w-80 h-80 rounded-full bg-brand-200/40 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container-x py-20 text-center">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 border border-emerald-200 text-emerald-800 text-sm font-medium mb-6">
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
      Online bestellen volgt binnenkort
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight">Bestel nu via <span style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #10b981, #047857); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; color: transparent;">WhatsApp</span></h1>
    <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-xl mx-auto">We rollen de webshop checkout binnenkort uit. Tot die tijd helpen we je persoonlijk via WhatsApp &mdash; snel, eerlijk en zonder gedoe.</p>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <a href="{{ wa_general }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-wa" style="padding: 1rem 2rem; font-size: 1.125rem;">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"/></svg>
        Chat op WhatsApp
      </a>
      <a href="/pages/telefoons" class="btn-outline">Bekijk telefoons
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-slate-500">Of bel ons op <a href="tel:+31624978746" class="font-semibold text-slate-800 hover:text-brand-700">+31 6 24978746</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="container-x py-16">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black tracking-tight text-center mb-10">Zo werkt het</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="card p-6 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="text-6xl font-black text-slate-100 absolute -top-2 right-4 select-none">1</div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 flex items-center justify-center mb-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="font-bold">Stuur je bericht</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Kies een telefoon en klik op &lsquo;Bestel via WhatsApp&rsquo;. We zien meteen welk model je wil.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="text-6xl font-black text-slate-100 absolute -top-2 right-4 select-none">2</div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 flex items-center justify-center mb-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="font-bold">Persoonlijk advies</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">We checken de voorraad, geven advies en bevestigen de prijs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="text-6xl font-black text-slate-100 absolute -top-2 right-4 select-none">3</div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 flex items-center justify-center mb-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="font-bold">Regelen &amp; leveren</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Samen regelen we de betaling en verzending. Klaar is Kees.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-center">
      <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-slate-50">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600 mx-auto mb-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        <span class="text-xs font-medium">6 maanden garantie</span>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-slate-50">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600 mx-auto mb-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="1" y="3" width="15" height="13"/><polygon points="16 8 20 8 23 11 23 16 16 16 16 8"/></svg>
        <span class="text-xs font-medium">Gratis verzending</span>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-slate-50">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600 mx-auto mb-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        <span class="text-xs font-medium">72-punten check</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

